  ('dietitian-moex-10724', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關膽汁之敘述，下列何者正確？ 由膽囊製造    胃液會促進膽汁由膽囊送到小腸 不會被肝腸循環再吸收回來   含有膽固醇、卵磷脂、膽色素等', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc2d54fbf051", "answer_pdf_sha1": "dfeb01e9d1ae", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10725', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-094-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關人體對澱粉的消化和吸收，下列敘述何者正確？ 由肝臟分泌澱粉 （Amylase）進行消化  澱粉經消化為單糖（如：乳糖）後，可由小腸黏膜吸收 果糖為單糖，經由一級主動運輸吸收  大部分的單糖經由二級主動運輸吸收', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "cc2d54fbf051", "answer_pdf_sha1": "dfeb01e9d1ae", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
